    • Constructor Detail

      • OrbitPattern

        public OrbitPattern(long amplitude,
                    long period,
                    long center)
        Construct a new orbit pattern. This pattern is a sinusoidal function y=a*sin(bx)+c, where the x-axis is the round number of takeoff and the the y-axis is the duration of flight to the nearest integer. The amplitude, period, and center are measured in rounds.
